atar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-57d06c97dd46a79bce1cd890f14880c0_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/fa0b7afd4910d4ab27894c639d7a253e","user_type":"people","headline":"白门楼上挂满了吕布的尸体","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561954834","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546021550,"updated_time":1546021550,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"content":"\u003cp\u003e数学系学渣强行回答一次\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你要是能在高中毕业前，也就是18岁前，证明哥德巴赫猜想，并且得到学术界认可\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那清华北大肯定会抢着你去\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当教授的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我本科的学校在美国算不上最顶尖也算是名校了，你让我们学校数学院本科毕业生，随便挑，保证都能看得懂问题啥意思，这算是个进步，因为我们有时候题目都能看的一脸懵逼，但是你让我们别说开个头，连找个稍微点的思路去尝试证明都不可能\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e感觉题主是被民科洗脑了，看的懂就觉得应该能解出来的问题，只存在于你上学考试的时代，对于真正的数学难题一点概念都没有，18岁前能靠自己证明哥德巴赫猜想，你去清北当教授，都属于为国家牺牲小我了，你这个智力要是再高点，都能被5常抢着去研究了，完全超出人类范畴了\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":564024529,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"fd4b70c7a1540bc525afab18e299c4f7","url_token":"jiabao-han","name":"Hamburger","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/5f8becec30df9ba33dd7735fff7ab34d_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/5f8becec30df9ba33dd7735fff7ab34d_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/fd4b70c7a1540bc525afab18e299c4f7","user_type":"people","headline":"如果我也能享受这一刻，我便是世界之王。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_