a488776235116321c5c1237","user_type":"people","headline":"业余物理爱好者，民科怼者，无神论者","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563774301","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-170f5161e58645ff0ea02c0257fcd826_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546275353,"updated_time":1546279108,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":14,"content":"\u003cp\u003e为什么还有这么多关注的人？我觉得吧，散了吧，指不定人家是宣传的，我这里给人家纠完错，空间啥的也帮人宣传了一波（可是为了防止空间好友被误导也不大想删了），指不定我们是被当成人家头像那种狒狒给当猴耍的呢？可惜就算知道，我觉得也得留着回复，省的误区没被纠正，难得啊，自愿的给钩进猴戏里了 \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其实我挺喜欢你理解负质数并把它当做工具来用，但是建议您别太自大，人都有中二的时候，希望你以后踏下心来学习，思维还是蛮不错的，但是您太过表演性人格了，建议多读书多看报，建议您能够戒了对科学的功利心\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-586107c6fd821b8f5fb4097421c0da0f_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1536\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-0f05fa3296db71dc20acded2a676e3e4_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1536\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-586107c6fd821b8f5fb4097421c0da0f_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1536'%20height='2048'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1536\" data-rawheight=\"2048\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-0f05fa3296db71dc20acded2a676e3e4_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1536\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-586107c6fd821b8f5fb4097421c0da0f_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-586107c6fd821b8f5fb4097421c0da0f_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561365968,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"4b51a540259dcb743e84231208353fed","url_token":"wang-yuan-13-52-38","name":"大总攻夜幕","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-839cfd3ed9080d1988306ba78830df18_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-839cfd3ed9080d1988306ba78830df18_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/4b51a540259dcb743e84231208353fed","user_type":"people","headline":"无业人员","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561365968","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545962431,"updated_time":1545962651,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":14,"content":"\u003cp\u003e谢邀。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e身为一个物理人士没有什么过多的评论可言。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是听说题主，要发布证明的那位需要投稿。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我可以很明确的告诉你，你这样大牛级的工作就应该投在nature，science这样的期刊上。如果你的英语水平不够，我可以帮你，给我个三作就好，我甚至还可以帮你修改论文的学术规范要求。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e也许，你将会是第一个得到菲尔兹奖的本土中国人。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这样我也能吃个瓜青史留名。    \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不谢。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e送我上去，让原po看到。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e…………切割线…………\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e后续，另外我在清华数学也有几位认识的教授。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果证明是真的，可以立刻帮你通知。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559795036,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"7bd7d0926c9097690af562e6160f2caf","url_token":"ivan-lam-50","name":"ivan lam","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/7bd7d0926c9097690af562e6160f2caf","user_type":"people","headline":"对未知充满好奇，Linux kernel程序员","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559795036","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545782215,"updated_time":1545782215,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"content":"\u003cp\u003e菲尔兹奖妥妥的，什么保送还清华北？至少是牛逼的大学教授等着。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561445618,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"bbb58b3cf74a5fa7e835c0358e430acf","url_token":"warmwine","name":"温酒","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-50617f64221aac69a4e586124cc04421_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-50617f64221aac69a4e586124cc04421_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/bbb58b3cf74a5fa7e835c0358e430acf","user_type":"people","headline":"微信公众号:hearmr333   公众号名称：\"温酒说\"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561445618","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545968163,"updated_time":1545968189,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":14,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我觉得可能王子屯大学会召唤你\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563784348,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"159de35381ffa57ff35dbdd4da99a2d1","url_token":"li-gou-bu-hai","name":"德拉根宝","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-348cc58edb5a7c2690bc1a1aa152f5be_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-348cc58edb5a7c2690bc1a1aa152f5be_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/159de35381ffa57ff35dbdd4da99a2d1","user_type":"people","headline":"进阶法律人","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563784348","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-9f2a3cb17817b87ee9fc471f2957fc30_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546276633,"updated_time":1546312099,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":16,"content":"\u003cp\u003e2019.1.1 11.02编辑\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他删文章了。据他所说，他“曾经我一度觉得自己证明出了这一猜想”，算是委婉承认自己错了？于是证明同学现在正表现出努力销号的样子给我们看。也许是为了躲些砖头，也许是接着炒冷饭。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e似乎有点失落啊，对于他，对于吃瓜的我们。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-17226e2b488030a16ab781baa4692342_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"713\" data-rawheight=\"596\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-385f79c13407271a04c5a9e5de907f20_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"713\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-17226e2b488030a16ab781baa4692342_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='713'%20height='596'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"713\" data-rawheight=\"596\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-385f79c13407271a04c5a9e5de907f20_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"713\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-17226e2b488030a16ab781baa4692342_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-17226e2b488030a16ab781baa4692342_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e他要是继续荡着，坚持不懈地说自己是对的，也许还是会有一群吃瓜群众给他赞给他好评呢，现在不还有3万多关注嘛。明明还可以自媒体再来一波，说不定可以身跻郭英森行列呢。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这么认怂，没意思呀。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过我也不想评论他了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在这新年第一天，我们看到了不少人心甘情愿为他造势起哄，心甘情愿被耍，心甘情愿被带节奏（也许证明出了呢），一起演同一场戏。好在这也就是一个无关紧要的提问而已，看了就看了，骗了就骗了嘛。只是，是不是还有其他类似的事情，在紧要的领域发生着呢。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过也有好的一面吧，这一次，朋友们应该认识到了，为什么那些知名学者教授不愿意以善意来面对这些“潜在的科学家”了。累。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e以下为原回答。\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e刚刚见到该高中生的回答了。我不知道内容正确与否，但我看到了一大堆人无视严谨科学正确与否直接给赞，才一个小时就为 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hash=\"7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\"\u003e@证明\u003c/a\u003e 积累了2000余赞，6000余评论。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我只看到了全民跨年的狂欢。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果说这是对一条评论点赞，可以理解为是对抖机灵开玩笑的赞许；但当这是对一个回答的评价时，抱着“厉害了”“嘲讽式点赞”的心态点赞，就是对自己点赞价值的侮辱。截至目前的六千多条评论，基本都是“前排”“留名”的评论，见不到几个有价值评论，也足见这种看客心理了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以我认为，“高中生证明哥猜能否保送清北”作为问题来说，回答是能（当然以这位高中生答出来为前提，这一点可以坐等稍后大牛的认真评论）；作为事件，凸显的是知乎对有价值问答的忽视、对这种流量事件的放纵。我的感觉是，流量跟泡沫一样，终将驱逐良币，毁灭市场。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e也许这是一种卫道士心理，毕竟大众喜欢啥我管不着吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-687bb0ce41b0ce2e437a5851f6a93813_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2244\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-6290a1dd0a21eec796a7d9307d0f886b_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-687bb0ce41b0ce2e437a5851f6a93813_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='2244'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2244\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-6290a1dd0a21eec796a7d9307d0f886b_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-687bb0ce41b0ce2e437a5851f6a93813_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-687bb0ce41b0ce2e437a5851f6a93813_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562409896,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"a4f1ecd306e06d9a72c1e7288c222516","url_token":"si-wang-dai-si","name":"痴情蛊灬DOM","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-844d4899677546a5f876a359d7175bf1_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-844d4899677546a5f876a359d7175bf1_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/a4f1ecd306e06d9a72c1e7288c222516","user_type":"people","headline":"老渣男，抖抖抖sss，DOM","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562409896","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546084252,"updated_time":1546084252,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":9,"content":"被禁言三天\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e第一天看到这个问题，我想回\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e我，哥德巴赫，打钱\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e第二天看到这个问题，我想回\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e你看高考把这孩子逼成啥样了\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e第三天看到这个问题，我想回\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e别让营销号找到套路就够了","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561222129,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b450e65e2ca7fd5996be6db49ad013a4","url_token":"qing-zheng-30-4","name":"青争","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/b450e65e2ca7fd5996be6db49ad013a4","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561222129","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-a2a1e58383020ca02430ea11700c376c_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545928207,"updated_time":1545928930,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":16,"content":"\u003cp\u003e1月1号见证哥德巴赫猜想猜想哈哈，虽然看了n多评论知道了成功几率差多为2的头发数次方分之一，但作为反向机会主义者（瞎编的）我觉得支持一个大家都觉得对的比较没意思。（哈哈哈假如我押对了相当于中了一个不可能得到超级彩票，不是说概率为0不等于不可能发生吗，手动狗头）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e知乎上吵翻天该鼓励或者打击这位同学，嘲讽他和嘲讽鼓励他的和嘲讽盲目嘲讽鼓励他的，再次笑话民科的，各位数学大牛发的也看不懂，假装收藏\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过我觉得真的证明出他的错了（万一对了）给个教训就好了，真的沸如江海的评论对于一个未成年来说，还能比较镇定，我叹服他的心理素质，起码这就是很多人做不到的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e下图我起码觉得他情商不错，正常高中生应该反驳或者暴跳如雷\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-39df2fc860977a8916335b16cc64b560_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-822e2e652b064d98f952e8970f75756a_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-39df2fc860977a8916335b16cc64b560_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='1920'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-822e2e652b064d98f952e8970f75756a_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-39df2fc860977a8916335b16cc64b560_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-39df2fc860977a8916335b16cc64b560_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5cc12a52148676a1dce0f5c38e5763a8_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b94a9150457450f7129d66374b6f305a_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5cc12a52148676a1dce0f5c38e5763a8_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='1920'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b94a9150457450f7129d66374b6f305a_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5cc12a52148676a1dce0f5c38e5763a8_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5cc12a52148676a1dce0f5c38e5763a8_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e很多人嘲讽有智商就不应该偏科，我对大脑没研究，但也知道历史上很多偏科成才的故事。为什么以前可以，现在不行？你可以嘲讽，但是觉得别人鼓励他就是在捧杀他，未免也太对青年人苛求了吧，键盘打字容易，别人有能力让这个话题火也是你们一做出来的，说到底，说他炒作，火还不得感谢你们？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我个人觉得某些回答大牛所用讽刺手法很有情商，人活久懂得“教训”晚辈还是挺不错的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":557294829,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0c39dee3bf4347415d4bcf08397a9866","url_token":"da-po-sha-guo-wen-dao-di-94-55","name":"打破砂锅问到底","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-83aedf6e28c074ca7b934779dcd7215d_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-83aedf6e28c074ca7b934779dcd7215d_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0c39dee3bf4347415d4bcf08397a9866","user_type":"people","headline":"真理，永远追求，永远不近，每揭开一层，都会引发我的狂喜","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/557294829","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545456040,"updated_time":1545456338,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":16,"content":"\u003cp\u003e      觉得你很有信心，不知道你的水平怎么样，但是你可以试试。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果你成功了，祝贺你在数学界站在了无数数学家的前头。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e没成功，也不会有人记得你的笑话。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是我希望你能从最基础的地方开始论证，数学不是靠想象，而是严格的逻辑命题，一个地方有问题就是整个理论的崩塌，所以望你能将自己的思维缕清，再找找自己的漏洞吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是你只是将其作为一个上名校的途径，你就错了。因为你这么想的话，实际上是用最困难的方法上清华，如果你真有解出哥德巴赫猜想的能力，那就要考虑清华是否配的上你这种数学大师了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e摆正态度吧，觉得做的对你就去做，错了就改。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563319903,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"85a19e5647b63576bb13afc746ca46ed","url_token":"type16cns","name":"不要邀请或者关注","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-65f9577db630595b01641ae9f01068fa_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-65f9577db630595b01641ae9f01068fa_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/85a19e5647b63576bb13afc746ca46ed","user_type":"people","headline":"看见ZZ我也会点赞的。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563319903","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-12fe278275eb4c5f893d5785756bda09_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546224889,"updated_time":1546281977,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":16,"content":"\u003cp\u003e仍然希望这一切是真的，真的证明成功了。虽然我是学计算机的，但是今天这个时间点，任何基础科学的一点点成就，都可以为人类的未来带来太多太多了。我很希望见到新的突破，尽管与我的专业无关，但是这事关人类未来。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其实这个问题之下我更希望见到一种观点，就是现在对于基础科学的投入仍然还有欠缺。因为基础科学太关键了，无论投入多少都不能说多，但是基础科学的本科生仍然不具有和传统行业在工资上叫板的资本。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e基础科学应该成为舆论热点。应该热起来。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e==========\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-c3f7b3bdcc15a4aa77796f4c0e0fd2ea_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1242\" data-rawheight=\"2208\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-536504b9d2c39dbd18dc1a13b49a0aec_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1242\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-c3f7b3bdcc15a4aa77796f4c0e0fd2ea_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1242'%20height='2208'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1242\" data-rawheight=\"2208\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-536504b9d2c39dbd18dc1a13b49a0aec_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1242\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-c3f7b3bdcc15a4aa77796f4c0e0fd2ea_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-c3f7b3bdcc15a4aa77796f4c0e0fd2ea_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-865d44d09410aa2d63bfda4e57ccf979_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"456\" data-rawheight=\"4096\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-61177338387b67205ab884cf8d8ce330_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"456\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-865d44d09410aa2d63bfda4e57ccf979_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='